      "raw": "The overall amplitude is set so V_FR(tau_0) = 3*H_0^2*Omega_Lambda",
      "type": "code",
      "context": "V_FR(tau) = V_tree(tau) + beta_flux * |omega_3|^2(tau) where beta_flux is chosen so V_FR has a minimum at tau_0 = 0.30.",
